Acting eThekwini Mayor, Fawzia Peer, can not say for certain if she was poisoned. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Acting eThekwini Mayor, Fawzia Peer can't say for certain if she was poisoned. She was rushed to hospital after drinking water at a council meeting. The water is being tested. Durban poison: Acting mayor rushed to hospital She says whatever the outcome she will continue doing her job. “It's the water that's always placed in council. Somehow this time the water I drank had a funny smell. The smell was kind of paraffin. I don't know who tried to do something. No matter what, it will not deter me. I am much stronger than before,” said Peer.